snippet.title: RoboGAL - DEMO Trailer
snippet.description:
RoboGAL demo is OUT!

We've released a demo with two complete levels that you can try out and enjoy whenever you want!

You can download the demo via this link and follow us on social media and keep up with RoboGAL news in the comments section!
